default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultEmployers want to secure a better balance between pay, performance and productivity. To deliver 
defaultthe
default aspirations for the prevention of ill
default-
defaulthealth and the delivery of seven
default-
defaultday care, national pay frameworks must be fit for
default purpose, fair to staff and offer the taxpayer the very best value for money. The NHS will be in a stronger position to maintain or increase staffing levels, and therefore protect jobs, if employers are able to make better use of their pay bill.
